'''''Outrider''-class cruisers''' were produced just before the time of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. Although they were designed as exploration ships, they packed the weaponry of [[Warship/Legends|warships]]. The [[Order of the Silver Jedi]] owned at least one of these ships, which they trapped the [[Force vampire|Force Vampire]] on until he was found by [[Captain/Legends|Captain]] [[Korsu]]'s picket ship.

